configure Ethernet Interfaces/Switching
show interfaces terse extensive

configure
edit interface ge-0/0/0
set vlan-tagging
edit unit 10
set vlan-id 10
edit family inet 
set address 10.0.0.2/24

top show | compare

***delete unit 0 (every unit need a vlan tag)


show route
